title: Golf course view! Enclosed backyard! Garages! Dog Parks!
posting_body: The apartment homes offer unique interiors including plank flooring, granite in the kitchen, faux stainless steel appliances, ceramic surface cook top, built-in bookshelves, tray ceilings, crown molding, ceiling fans with lights, decorative fireplaces and full-size washer/dryers.

Spectacular amenities include resort-style pool and fountains, pavilion with picnic tables and BBQ, indoor racquetball and basketball, fitness center with HDTV, sand volleyball, playground, enclosed backyards, game room and business center with high-speed Internet.
